\subsection{Data Partitioning}{

Observations are classified into two groups:

\deqn{
\text{period} =
\begin{cases}
\text{Drought}, & t \in [t_{start}, t_{end}] \\
\text{Non-drought}, & \text{otherwise}
\end{cases}
}
